		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="423" height="85" d:userLabel="仆↓人进行至多5段的普通攻击，其依次造成2" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">仆人向前扔出镰刀，造成<span color="#ff9999">70%</span><span>伤害，接着仆人顺势利用链条冲出，造成</span><span color="#ff9999">70%+50%</span><span>伤害，之后接上数刀挥舞。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="959" width="439" height="114" d:userLabel="仆↓人进行至多5段的普通攻击，其依次造成2" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">仆人进行至多5段的普通攻击，其依次造成<span color="#ff9999">30%,40%,40%,40%x2,80%</span><span>伤害，其中第一段会丢出旋转火轮，将持续造成</span><span color="#ff9999">12.5%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1183" width="424" height="114" d:userLabel="仆↓人进行至多5段的普通攻击，其依次造成2" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">若玩家处于仆人侧后方，则仆人立即进行转身斩，造成<span color="#ff9999">50%x2</span><span>伤害，然后追加施放「月染狱中翩跹」或「朱丝织缀之礼」。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/仆人2.assets/Image_15.png')" x="1392" y="138">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/仆人2.assets/Image_16.png')" x="722" y="873">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/仆人2.assets/Image_17.png')" x="719" y="1097">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ad4218" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#ad4218">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1104" width="439" height="174" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">仆人施放有关于生命之契的技能后，会消耗自身<span color="#ffccbf">1.5%</span><span>生命值(生命值&lt;20%消耗当前</span><span color="#ffbfbf">7.5%</span><span>生命值)，若该攻击命中玩家则恢复</span><span color="#ffccbf">3%</span><span>生命值；右侧</span><span color="#ff7272">红色</span><span>的伤害代表其会施加「生命之契」，该攻击命中生命之契下的玩家时，造成的伤害会提升</span><span color="#ffb299">150%</span><span>。<br/><br/>「生命之契」：消除生命之契后将使队伍中前台角色获得「赤叶」效果，角色进行重击将产生「血汐冲击」造成真实伤害，并消耗「赤叶」效果，该效果至多叠加1层。<br/>「血汐冲击」造成基于仆人</span><span color="#ffccbf">1.8%</span><span>生命值的真实伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="438" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">入战后，仆人立即从高处跃下，下落至玩家处，造成<span color="#ff4c4c">100%</span><span>伤害，并秀出她的双镰刀。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="735" width="440" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">仆人用双镰刀划出X，展开绞割领域，造成<span color="#ff4c4c">50%</span><span>伤害，领域内持续进行绞割，持续造成</span><span color="#ff4c4c">20%,10%</span><span>伤害，最后领域爆裂，造成</span><span color="#ff4c4c">40%+100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="959" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">仆人展开外骨骼，发动血火之光，造成<span color="#ff4c4c">100%</span><span>伤害，可以连续施放至多3次。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="437" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">仆人施放 「血潮赤宴」类技能之前，会打响指，为角色施加<span textDecoration="underline">「生命之契」</span><span>并进入 「血潮赤宴」蓄力状态。打断蓄力则反噬仆人</span><span color="#ffccbf">11.2%</span><span>的生命值。生命之契的大小基于仆人</span><span color="#bfffff">10%</span><span>的攻击力，并且每2.5秒流失</span><span color="#bfffff">(1.25%HP+200)</span><span>的生命值。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
