		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="735" width="399" height="114" d:userLabel="仆↓人进行至多5段的普通攻击，其依次造成2" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">仆人掷手地面，唤出深血木丛，造成<span color="#ff4c4c">75%</span><span>伤害，之后扩散至外圈，也造成</span><span color="#ff4c4c">75%</span><span>伤害，最后仆人回收一掷，造成</span><span color="#ff4c4c">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/仆人2.assets/Image_24.png')" x="719" y="649">
		</BitmapImage>
